<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Food Delivery Service</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <section id="about">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <div class="about-content">
            <p>
                Welcome to Food Delivery Service, your number one source for delicious and freshly prepared meals delivered right to your doorstep. We're dedicated to giving you the very best of culinary experiences, with a focus on quality, customer service, and uniqueness.
            </p>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                Our mission is to make good food easily accessible to everyone. We believe that everyone deserves to enjoy high-quality, nutritious meals without the hassle of cooking and cleaning up. We strive to bring you the best food delivery experience possible by using fresh ingredients, innovative recipes, and sustainable practices.
            </p>
            <h2>Our Vision</h2>
            <p>
                We envision a world where healthy, delicious food is available at the click of a button, empowering people to live better and healthier lives. We aim to be the leading food delivery service known for our commitment to quality, convenience, and sustainability.
            </p>
            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Quality:</strong> We are committed to providing high-quality meals made from the freshest ingredients.</li>
                <li><strong>Customer Satisfaction:</strong> Our customers are at the heart of everything we do. We strive to exceed their expectations with every order.</li>
                <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> We continuously seek innovative ways to improve our services and offer unique culinary experiences.</li>
                <li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> We are dedicated to sustainable practices that minimize our environmental impact and promote a healthier planet.</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
            <p>
                Our team is a diverse group of passionate individuals who share a love for food and a commitment to excellence. From our talented chefs to our dedicated customer service representatives, each member plays a crucial role in delivering the best possible experience to our customers.
            </p>
            <div class="team-members">
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="/images/chef.jpg" alt="Chef">
                    <h3>John Doe</h3>
                    <p>Head Chef</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="/images/manager.jpg" alt="Manager">
                    <h3>Jane Smith</h3>
                    <p>Operations Manager</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="/images/customer-service.jpg" alt="Customer Service">
                    <h3>Emily Johnson</h3>
                    <p>Customer Service Lead</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
